entries.femaleVariant: Can we pleeease stop talking about work?

<kiroshi l="rus" o="А о чём ещё говорить? О красивых бабах?" t="Well... what else is there to talk about? Smoking hot babes?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="rus" o="Помнишь новенькую из контроля качества?" t="You know that new chick from QA?" b="" a=""/>
You mean that blonde with the Kiroshies – the one by the window?
